				<wikidot:authorName>Communism will win</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>617958</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>The problem is that you used dithering when making the gradients, which basically adds a ton of visual noise that isn't visible to the naked eye, but makes PNG compression much less effective. <a href="https://i.gyazo.com/16d93ed222d9ead15401b16654451dbf.png">Here's an exaggerated version</a> to highlight the problem.</p> <p>I've uploaded a file named &quot;healing2.png&quot; to the page; it's pretty much the same image, except I've made the gradients a lot smoother. It's about 220kb.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
